Kannywood actor and director Ali Nuhu has sued musician and actor, Adam A. Zango over alleged defamation and assassination of character. Daily Trust found out that Nuhu sued Zango on Thursday before USC Fagge in Kano state. According to the court summon obtained by Daily Trust, Zango was invited to appear before the court by 8:30am on Monday 15th April, 2019. It would be recalled that there was no love lost between the duo for the past three months and all efforts to reconcile them proved abortive. Kannywood Verified: Adam Zango joins Ali Nuhu, Rahama Sadau, Hadiza Gabon, others Kannywood’s Adam Zango battles people who insult his mum Adam Zango says he dated Nafeesat for 3 years